{
  "stem": "25831.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we saw the house and the forest, and it wasn't quite as mysterious and romantic as I had pictured it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But I was very glad to have been there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I remember the day she left our employ, which was May 8, 1931.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "She-- And we took her to the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I tried to suppress my tears as much as I could.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But I have the feeling I wasn't too successful.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "She came back to visit next year for my bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "In other words, I was nearly 12 when she left, but she came for the bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And that she was the most important person for me at the bar mitzvah, with the exception of one other person whom I will bring up later.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Coming back to my early childhood, I did not experience anti-Semitism until when I was five years old and I was walking with my governess.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was bouncing a ball, and the ball rolled ahead of me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I ran after to retrieve it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And a man saw me pick up the ball and said to me, what do you want, you little Jewboy?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so I didn't even know what it all meant.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when I came home, I told my father about it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my father says, well, this man was an anti-Semite.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so I said, what does all this mean?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so that was the first time really that I heard about or experienced anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when I started school, when I was little under 6-- the school year started in April.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was unaware of any anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the teacher I had was a Lutheran who observed Martin's Day, which was Martin Luther's Day.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And on that day, certain sweet rolls were brought to school.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
